The biggest, goodest and bestest Power of Krynn! Almost everybody likes Paladine, except some then. There's always someone out there that ruins everything for everyone. - Kender Child explaining Krynn mythology
Paladine dwells in Solania, the fifth heaven of Celestia, in a Realm called the Dome of Creation. 

